[metadata]
Name:Fecundity — whenever a creature dies, its controller may draw
Goal:Win
Turns:3
Difficulty:Medium
Description:P1 controls Fecundity ("Whenever a creature dies, that creature's controller may draw a card."). P2 (the fixed controller) burns P1's Llanowar Elves with Blaze. When the Elves dies, Fecundity's broad "a creature dies" trigger fires and P1 — the DYING creature's controller — draws a card. Regression for mtg-913 B12 (the dies-trigger parser previously only handled Card.Self / Card.EquippedBy / Creature.DamagedBy and silently dropped the broad ValidCard$ Creature shape).

